name: Hatsune Miku: Project Diva Extend
description: Hatsune Miku: Project DIVA Extend is the third game in the Project DIVA series and the last to be released on the PlayStation Portable. It acts as an expansion of Hatsune Miku: Project DIVA 2nd, utilizing the exact same gameplay and adding a selection of nine new songs, including modules and music videos to go along with them.
